# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GREENLOOP .gitignore
# Leading "/" anchors a pattern to the repository root; patterns without
# it match at any depth. Trailing "/" matches directories only.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── private research material — must NEVER be published ────────────────
# Scraped social/community study data (Reddit threads, vendor articles).
# Contains third-party usernames and verbatim posts; local reference only.
/internal/

# ── secrets & environment ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Defense in depth: this repo needs no env files or keys, so anything
# matching these patterns is a mistake — keep it out of history.
.env
.env.*
*.env
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.crt
*.csr
id_rsa
id_ed25519
*.token
credentials.json
service-account*.json
secrets.*
.netrc
.npmrc

# ── GREENLOOP runtime state ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Created by Phase 1 when an agent works *in* this repo. It is a local
# audit trail (state.json, plan.md, memory.md, worklog.md); only commit
# it deliberately, never by default.
.greenloop/

# ── installer / injector artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────
# Backups written before any file replacement (install.sh `place()`,
# greenloop-inject.ts marker merges).
*.bak

# ── JavaScript runtime artifacts ────────────────────────────────────────
# Running the TUI (`bun greenloop-inject.ts`) auto-installs @opentui/core,
# which creates these next to the script. The repo itself has no deps.
node_modules/
bun.lockb
bun.lock
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

# ── editor & OS noise ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/

# ── logs & scratch ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.tmp
/tmp/
/scratch/

# ── legacy file locations ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Pre-reorganization copies kept on disk for reference. The canonical,
# maintained versions live in workflow/, cli/, and docs/. These three
# entries match ONLY the root-level originals, not the new directories.
/src/
/greenloop-inject.ts
/DEPLOY.md
